(41, 'lokab1mtnqenzgu6wde3', '2x67y138g5wfwm1mxo3d', 'yo24qijf5nmpaxno7il6', 'Chillies', '', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Drench the nursery beds with Copper Oxy Chloride @ 3g or Metalaxyl @ 3g per liter of water to control damping off.</li>\r\n	<li>Prevailing weather conditions are congenial for incidence of Choanephora blight, wilt and powdery mildew.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n'),
